    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>News</h2>
        <p>
            In latest update have been add following features:<br>
            Changes commit:  …<br>
            graph getData finished<br>
            graph getData async done<br>
            graph client signals drawed<br>
            menu small style changes<br>
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://192.168.2.13/Home/News">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Link to old users.nordit.cz</h2>
        <p>If you need old users click below</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://users.nordit.cz/">Bye &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
</div>
